**Approach:**
* Loop from i=len/2 i.e half of the string.
* Check if a substring of length 'i' can be appended integer no of times to form the given string.(i.e check if len%i == 0.
* Take a substring sub from index 0 to i-1.
* Append the substring sub len/i times to a string builder st.
* if st.toString()==s,return true else i--
* Do this till i>=1.
![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/f058ffaf-3b0c-4f42-b831-c53d8a8515eb_1656934628.3738313.jpeg)
